	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I don't expect to adjust everything on the fly like I do with the bar that hides scrolling glitches. I could probably have the music adapt itself on the fly as well, but the physics and such would be kinda hard to do. I'm not sure I will change any of the physics for PAL though, because the rounding errors could end up making the game play too differently from the NTSC version... But it would be very nice to have everything in a single ROM.

		

